Use Devika AI
Create a Python script to test Devika AI. Hereâ€™s a basic example assuming Devika AI provides a Python library.

Create a Python script: Open your terminal and create a new Python script.
 
 
nano main.py
Add the following code:
 
 
import devika

# Initialize Devika AI with your API key
api_key = "YOUR_API_KEY"
ai = devika.initialize(api_key=api_key)

# Example usage
response = ai.chat("Hello, how can I help you today?")
print(response)
Replace YOUR_API_KEY with the actual API key you obtained.
Run Your Script
Run your Python script to see Devika AI in action.

 
 
  main.py
